I've decided what to do on holidays. Will take a car, and drive. Spain, France, Italy, Slovenia, Croatia, Greece, Turkey, Bolgaria, Romania, Slovakia, Poland, Germany, Netherland, Belgium, France(again), Spain(finally). I'm fed up with my living in a hole, I'm young, I have time, I have money, I've got a car, I like driving (night driving), I do what I want, I give no explanations, I'm alive, I'm on the run, follow me!
If you live or would like to go to any of this countries is always possible to meet somewhere in the space and time, hitch hike me, I'll take you. We will never run out of petrol.
